java.io.Serializable
public class Book
extends Publication

The Book class represents book entities and is subclass of Publication.

Besides attributes provided by Publication, publisherName and publishPlace is provided by Book class.

Initialises a newly created Book object with attributes of the passed parameters.

Parameters:
IDNumber - ID number of a Book, which is the primary key of a Book, and is in format of "BK0000".
publicationTitle - Title of this Book.
authorSet - A Set of author's full names, which may not be recorded in this system.
publishDate - The date this Book is published, namely, is uploaded to this system. And is in Date type.
publisherName - The publisher's name of this Book.
publishPlace - The place where this Book is published.
uploaderUserName - The userName of the one who uploads this Book.
